Package: epos
Type: Package
Title: Epilepsy Ontology Similarities
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Bernd Mueller
Maintainer: Bernd Mueller <bernd.mueller@zbmed.de>
Description: Ranked result lists of neurological drug names co-occurring with named entities from the epilepsy ontologies EpSO, ESSO, and EPILONT are aggregated in order to generate an overview table of drugs that are relevant to epilepsy. The alignment of the Top-K Ranked Lists was conducted using the R-package TopKLists <https://cran.r-project.org/package=TopKLists>. The source data to create the ranked lists of drug names is produced using the text mining workflows described in  Müller, Bernd and Hagelstein, Alexandra (2016) <doi:10.4126/FRL01-006408558> and Müller, Bernd et al. (2017) <doi:10.1007/978-3-319-58694-6_22>.
